cancellationPolicies.label: Free Cancellation rates
cancellationPolicies.description: If you cancel your booking before 23:59 1st Dec 2025 (AEDT) your deposit will be refunded to your payment card. If you cancel after 23:59 1st Dec 2025 (AEDT) or in the event of a no-show, your deposit will not be refunded and the total of the first night's accommodation will be charged to your payment card, unless otherwise stated (see 'Things to Note' information). Please note that cancellations must be made directly within your booking in My Account.

cancellationPolicies.label: Non-refundable rates
cancellationPolicies.description: Your booking is non-refundable. If you choose to cancel your booking, or in the case of a no-show, you will still be charged the full cost of your booking.

dorms.name: Superior 10 Bed Mixed Dorm
dorms.description: Dormitory style and range in size from 2 beds upwards.  They offer mixed accommodation.
dorms.labelDescription: Spacious, stylish, and made for connection. This 10-bed dorm is all about laid-back group energy with privacy curtains, charging ports, and lockable storage to keep things easy.

paymentProcedure.label: Deposit only

Deposit only

paymentProcedure.label: Non-refundable
